Usage: createExclusiveGroups [-help] [<groupName>] [-gap <float>]
                             [-min_gap <float>] [-exclusiveGroups <string> | -mutuallyExclusiveGroups <string>]

-help                                 # Prints out the command usage
<groupName>                           # Specify one group name
                                      # (string, optional)
-exclusiveGroups <string>             # Specify groups which need to be
                                      # excluded (string, optional)
-gap <float>                          # Specify gap value. (float, optional)
-min_gap <float>                      # Specify the min_gap value
                                      # (float, optional)
-mutuallyExclusiveGroups <string>     # Specify groups which need to be
                                      # excluded with each other. This option
                                      # can be used independently
                                      # (string, optional)